          <li><a href="http://www.laoex.org/">The National Agricultural Extension and Forestry Extension Service (NAFES)</a></li>
          <li><a href="http://github.com/jokke/laofab/">Source code of LaoFAB repository on GitHub</a></li>
        </ul>
      </li>
          
      <li>
        <h3>Environment</h3>

        <ul>
            <li>Location: <code>/home/jokke/perl/LaoFAB</code></li>
            <li>Template engine: <code>[% settings.template %]</code></li>
            <li>Logger: <code>[% settings.logger %]</code></li>
            <li>Environment: <code>[% settings.environment %]</code></li>
        </ul>

      </li>
    </ul>

  </div>

